Show the root window.

The showroot command shows the root window. The unshowroot command puts the windows back how they were.

Here FOO is an arbitrary file name that you should supply, for instance, $HOME/.rpfdump.

---
What are some examples of useful things to put in your root window?

    XPhoon ( http://xphoon.sourceforge.net/ ) is an essential for lycanthropes.

by twb
